  <brief_title>ECG Signal Collection From Long QT Syndrome, Wide QRS Complexes, Heart Failure, and Cardiac Resynchronization Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Further Research on Human Feasibility of a Subcutaneous Implantable Defibrillator (S-ICD)- ECG Signal Collections From Various Patient Groups Whilst Attending Outpatient Follow-up</official_title>
  <sponsors>
